{
  "stem": "935.9",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they came to us, they were already 48 hours on the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is why they were so late, because the bridges were already blown up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the end of the war, and everything was very hard to get through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to us, and heard-- I saw the American cap, and I heard somebody say, does anybody speak English here?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there he was, an American.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can you imagine it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Outside of a German concentration camp, the war still going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was incredible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put us on the cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were supposed to go first to Lubeck, which was open city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In other words, on the Geneva Conference, not to be bombed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From there to Denmark, and then to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told us that it was very hard to get to us, so we had to leave immediately.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had some of the wounded there, who were sitting in front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now if-- whenever there is a Red Cross transport, what is supposed to be done, the commander goes-- commandant down goes to the radio and says, attention, attention now. 700 women are leaving Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They will go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will travel this and this route.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this route is not supposed to be bombed or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started travelling, and within five minutes, there were German tanks and artillery mixing between our Red Cross cars, which had plenty of Red Crosses.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had more than we, trying to assure a safe retreat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, we have to lose them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We cannot go with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going to be bombed if they stay with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we went into a forest, the Swedish leader, and we spent the entire night in that forest.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
